petrinet - package petrinet
This package contains classes and interfaces for simulating and working with Petri Networks.
PetriNet - module PetriNet
 
PetriNetwork - Class in petrinet
The 'PetriNetwork' class represents a Petri net with places, transitions, and arcs.
PetriNetwork() - Constructor for class petrinet.PetriNetwork
Constructs a new empty PetriNetwork.
PetriNetwork(List<Place>, List<Transition>, List<Arc>) - Constructor for class petrinet.PetriNetwork
Constructs a new PetriNetwork with specified lists of places, transitions, and arcs.
Place - Class in petrinet
The 'Place' class represents a location in a Petri net where tokens can be stored.
Place(int) - Constructor for class petrinet.Place
Constructs a new Place with a specified initial number of tokens.
Place(int, List<Arc>) - Constructor for class petrinet.Place
Constructs a new Place with a specified initial number of tokens and associated arcs.
